    %% Architecture Dependency & Structural Mappings
    Main ..> GamePanel : Instantiates
    
    GamePanel *--> GameWorld : Aggregates model
    GamePanel *--> GameEngine : Owns loop agent
    GamePanel *--> GameInputListener : Dispatches pointer inputs
    
    GameEngine --> GamePanel : Updates state flags / repaints UI
    GameEngine --> GameWorld : Drives periodic tick delta updates
    
    GameInputListener --> GamePanel : Mutates selection indexes & overlays
    GameInputListener --> GameWorld : Resolves resource collection / plant positioning

    %% Collections Managed by the GameWorld Container
    GameWorld "1" o--> "*" Plant : Tracks grid array cells
    GameWorld "1" o--> "*" Zombie : Manages lane lists
    GameWorld "1" o--> "*" Pea : Steps projectiles
    GameWorld "1" o--> "*" Sun : Pools resource objects
    GameWorld "1" o--> "*" Explosion : Ticks custom animations
    GameWorld "1" o--> "*" FloatText : Displays dynamic state labels

    %% Object Factories / Blueprints
    Plant --> PlantType : Tracks design template properties
    Zombie --> ZombieType : Tracks design template properties
    PlantType ..> Plant : Creates
    ZombieType ..> Zombie : Creates

    %% Inheritances
    Plant <|-- Sunflower
    Plant <|-- Peashooter
    Plant <|-- Wallnut
    Plant <|-- SnowPea
    Plant <|-- CherryBomb

    Zombie <|-- NormalZombie
    Zombie <|-- FastZombie
    Zombie <|-- TankZombie
    Zombie <|-- CherryZombie